Description: Package for evaluating user-specified finite stage policies and learning optimal treatment policies via doubly robust loss functions. Policy learning methods include doubly robust blip/CATE learning and sequential policy tree learning. The package also include methods for optimal subgroup analysis. See Nordland and Holst (2022) <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2212.02335> for documentation and references.
